1. Definitions

1.1. "This License" refers to the contents of this file.

1.2. "Shaderpack" refers to any software package that can be loaded by the Minecraft mod "OptiFine" or any compatible alternatives (such as Iris).

1.3. "This Shaderpack" refers to the all of the files and contents of said files that were packaged with This License.

1.4. "Normal Use" refers to Minecraft gameplay and/or creation and distribution of non-interactive content (such as, but not limited to: videos, images, etc.).

1.5. "Code" refers to any data that is intended to be interpreted by computers and/or the ideas behind said data.

1.6. "Small Portions", in the context of a Shaderpack, refers to less than one third of the contents or ideas that originated in said Shaderpack.

1.7. "Substantial Portions", in the context of a Shaderpack, refers to more than one third of the contents or ideas that originated in said Shaderpack.

1.8. "What42" refers to the creator of What42's Shader Base, which can be found at https://github.com/What42Pizza/What42s-Shader-Base.



